54:04.320 --> 54:07.840
You are the gunas and You are beyond the gunas.

54:08.000 --> 54:10.840
You are the body and You are beyond the body.

54:10.999 --> 54:14.040
You are the essence of time and You are beyond time.

54:14.999 --> 54:18.999
